repositories.name: stock-analysis-platform
repositories.description: AI-powered Indian stock analysis platform integrating Google Gemini for intelligent investment recommendations with real-time NSE/BSE data. Features portfolio management with INR support, technical indicators, interactive visualizations, and role-based access for analysts and investors. Built with Next.js, React, MongoDB, and NextAuth.js.

repositories.name: task-manager-server
repositories.description: A robust RESTful API for managing tasks and subtasks with user authentication, built with Node.js and Express. This backend service provides comprehensive task organization features and is deployed as serverless functions on Netlify.
